{"id":99,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":99,"title":"D&C 95","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 95"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Kirtland, Ohio, June 1, 1833. This revelation is a continuation of divine directions to build a house for worship and instruction, the house of the Lord (see",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.119-136"},"section 88:119–136"],")."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1-6"},"1–6"],", The Saints are chastened for their failure to build the house of the Lord;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.7-10"},"7–10"],", The Lord desires to use His house to endow His people with power from on high;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.11-17"},"11–17"],", The house is to be dedicated as a place of worship and for the school of the Apostles."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1","order":"06.05.095.12130"},["b","1"],"Verily, thus saith the Lord unto you whom I love, and whom I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"love"],"I also chasten that their sins may be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"forgiven"],", for with the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"chastisement"],"I prepare a way for their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"deliverance"],"in all things out of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"temptation"],", and I have loved you—"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.2","order":"06.05.095.12131"},["b","2"],"Wherefore, ye must needs be chastened and stand rebuked before my face;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.3","order":"06.05.095.12132"},["b","3"],"For ye have sinned against me a very grievous sin, in that ye have not considered the great commandment in all things, that I have given unto you concerning the building of mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"house"],";"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.4","order":"06.05.095.12133"},["b","4"],"For the preparation wherewith I design to prepare mine apostles to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"prune"],"my vineyard for the last time, that I may bring to pass my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"strange act"],", that I may",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"pour out"],"my Spirit upon all flesh—"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.5","order":"06.05.095.12134"},["b","5"],"But behold, verily I say unto you, that there are many who have been ordained among you, whom I have called but few of them are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"chosen"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.6","order":"06.05.095.12135"},["b","6"],"They who are not chosen have sinned a very grievous sin, in that they are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"walking"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"darkness"],"at noon-day."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.7","order":"06.05.095.12136"},["b","7"],"And for this cause I gave unto you a commandment that you should call your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"solemn assembly"],", that your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"fastings"],"and your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"mourning"],"might come up into the ears of the Lord of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"Sabaoth"],", which is by interpretation, the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"creator"],"of the first day, the beginning and the end."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.8","order":"06.05.095.12137"},["b","8"],"Yea, verily I say unto you, I gave unto you a commandment that you should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"build"],"a house, in the which house I design to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"endow"],"those whom I have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"chosen"],"with power from on high;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.9","order":"06.05.095.12138"},["b","9"],"For this is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"promise"],"of the Father unto you; therefore I command you to tarry, even as mine apostles at Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.10","order":"06.05.095.12139"},["b","10"],"Nevertheless, my servants sinned a very grievous sin; and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"contentions"],"arose in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"school"],"of the prophets; which was very grievous unto me, saith your Lord; therefore I sent them forth to be chastened."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.11","order":"06.05.095.12140"},["b","11"],"Verily I say unto you, it is my will that you should build a house.",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"If"],"you keep my commandments you shall have power to build it."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.12","order":"06.05.095.12141"},["b","12"],"If you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"keep"],"not my commandments, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"love"],"of the Father shall not continue with you, therefore you shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"walk"],"in darkness."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.13","order":"06.05.095.12142"},["b","13"],"Now here is wisdom, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"mind"],"of the Lord—let the house be built, not after the manner of the world, for I give not unto you that ye shall live after the manner of the world;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.14","order":"06.05.095.12143"},["b","14"],"Therefore, let it be built after the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"manner"],"which I shall show unto three of you, whom ye shall appoint and ordain unto this power."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.15","order":"06.05.095.12144"},["b","15"],"And the size thereof shall be fifty and five feet in width, and let it be sixty-five feet in length, in the inner court thereof."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.16","order":"06.05.095.12145"},["b","16"],"And let the lower part of the inner court be dedicated unto me for your sacrament offering, and for your preaching, and your fasting, and your praying, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"offering"],"up of your most holy desires unto me, saith your Lord."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.17","order":"06.05.095.12146"},["b","17"],"And let the higher part of the inner court be dedicated unto me for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"school"],"of mine apostles, saith Son",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"Ahman"],"; or, in other words, Alphus; or, in other words, Omegus; even Jesus Christ your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"Lord"],". Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1a","order":"06.05.095.12147"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.14"},"2 Sam. 7:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/13.18"},"Prov. 13:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.6.5-12"},"Heb. 12:6 (5–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/15.3"},"Hel. 15:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.4.4-5"},"D&C 101:4 (4–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.4"},"103:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastening"},"TG Chastening"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1b","order":"06.05.095.12149"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1c","order":"06.05.095.12151"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.2.1-8"},"Deut. 11:2 (1–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/105.6"},"D&C 105:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1d","order":"06.05.095.12153"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/14.14"},"2 Sam. 14:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.13"},"1 Cor. 10:13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1e","order":"06.05.095.12155"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temptation"},"TG Temptation"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.3a","order":"06.05.095.12157"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.8"},"Hag. 1:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.119"},"D&C 88:119"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.4a","order":"06.05.095.12159"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.61.61-75"},"Jacob 5:61 (61–75)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.19"},"D&C 24:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.3.3-4"},"33:3 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.17"},"39:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.4b","order":"06.05.095.12161"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/28.21"},"Isa. 28:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.95"},"D&C 101:95"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.4c","order":"06.05.095.12163"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/1.23"},"Prov. 1:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.27"},"Ezek. 36:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.28"},"Joel 2:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/2.17"},"Acts 2:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.38"},"D&C 19:38"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.5a","order":"06.05.095.12165"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/20.16"},"Matt. 20:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.31"},"D&C 63:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/105.36.35-36"},"105:36 (35–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.34.34-40"},"121:34 (34–40)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/election"},"Election"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worthiness"},"Worthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.6a","order":"06.05.095.12167"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.6b","order":"06.05.095.12169"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.29.15-45"},"Deut. 28:29 (15–45)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.7a","order":"06.05.095.12171"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.117.70-119"},"D&C 88:117 (70–119)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/solemn-assembly"},"TG Solemn Assembly"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.7b","order":"06.05.095.12173"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.7c","order":"06.05.095.12175"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.7d","order":"06.05.095.1217